Step 1 : install redux toolkit and react-redux packages
npm install @reduxjs/toolkit  - provide createSlice and configurStore
npm install react-redux - provide Provider component and Hooks to access and udpate state

Step 2 : Create folder struture 
index.js
store.js 
component - counter redux

Step 3 : create slice in store.js file and use configureStore to create store and export it

Step 4 : in index.js use Provider component to provide store to the app


Step 5 :  in any component, use useSelector to access state and useDispatch to update state
AND also use actions for dispatching actions, and dont forget to call it.